<a href="#" class="vote-for-comment" voteDirection="1" dd="x"><img style="position:relative;top:3px;opacity:0.35;" src="//codeforces.com/codeforces.org/s/74018/images/actions/comment-voteup-blue.png" alt="Vote: I like it" title="Vote: I like it"/></a>
